title: The Oaths "Desorden" - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track Of The Week
description:
The single "Desorden" by The Oaths is our next "Track of the Week" feature from Converse Rubber Tracks Mexico City. The band typically produced their own music, but having the input of a Rubber Tracks engineer helped them incorporate new ideas into their recording process.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
